secubox-smtp-relay (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release — SMTP relay module for SecuBox.
  * FastAPI backend with Postfix management endpoints.
  * Web interface with P31 Phosphor light theme.
  * Queue management (view, flush, delete).
  * Smarthost configuration with SASL authentication.
  * TLS encryption support.
  * Test email functionality.
  * Mail log viewing.
  * Auto-refresh dashboard (30 seconds).

